    "content": "The Bay Area Open Mixer happened yesterday — and what an evening it was. 🌉\n\nIIT Delhi alumni, founders, technologists, investors, and builders, came together at Los Altos, carrying the Institute with them, as they always do.\n\nThe same energy that began on the IIT Delhi campus filled a home thousands of miles away.\n\nThis is what the global IIT Delhi community looks like: alumni who give back through their time, their ideas, their networks, and their belief in the Institute that shaped them. 🧡\n\n#IITDelhi #IITDelhiAlumni #BayArea #SiliconValley #AlumniMeetup #SiliconValley #AlumniMeetup Ranjeeta Nanda Harsh Nanda Sashi Reddi Rajiv K. Mohit Aron Rohit Dube Nimisha Srivastava Anshuman Roy IIT Delhi Alumni Relations & Endowment Fund",
